\fBmain/main.c\fP
T}	T{
CLI entry point. Creates \fBstruct cmdline_data\fP and
\fBstruct global_data\fP, records start times, reads the parameter file
argument when \fBGETPARAM\fP is disabled, and runs \fBStartRun\fP,
\fBMainLoop\fP, then \fBEndRun\fP\&.
T}
